
maa ne pati patni ki randiya bana di apni ghar ke darwaze ko saja diya hai kuch ho gaya
chhota khargosh hone laga uski maa boli kyu rote ho ho hame
uski maa boli kyu rote ho ho hame vatan ka kya bana deti hai
udati patang dheere dheere neeche aa gayi khargosh ke bache ne tumko dekha
muniya o raju buttonwood aa rahi hai teri patang ko chali gayi patang yeh to pay
maniyani suits had kardiya patang choot ke bare mein uski
raju ek bass leke aaya uchak uchak kar paisa patang udane ki koshish ki lekin was mahatma jayegi
chidiya apne chote bache ko nahi kar rahi hai bache ko nahi milta lag raha hai na jaane kahan kamlo